Alternative, use custom `Pair` class that implements `Comparable`.

```
class Pair implements Comparable&lt;Pair&gt; {
    Integer value;
    Integer index;

    public Pair(Integer value, Integer index) {
        this.value = value;
        this.index = index;
    }

    @Override
    public int compareTo(Pair o) {
        return value - o.value;
    }
}
